Requirements Document
â€˜Visionâ€™
To create an AI-powered voice conversation trainer that makes elite communication training accessible for professionals. The system enables users (such as salespeople, healthcare workers, and job seekers) to practice high-stakes conversations with realistic, customizable AI personas in a private, always-available environment.

Functional Requirements
Core Features (MVP)
1. Voice Conversation Engine
â€¢	Real-time speech-to-text (STT) processing (Google Cloud STT).
â€¢	Natural language understanding and conversation flow (LLM like Qwen2.5-0.5B).
â€¢	Text-to-speech (TTS) with emotional variation (e.g Coqui TTS).
â€¢	Supports multiple back-and-forth exchanges between the user and the AI rather than just responding to a single question or statement.
â€¢	Conversation context memory.
2. Persona System
â€¢	Pre-built personas (e.g., aggressive, indecisive, skeptical).
â€¢	Persona behaviour consistency across sessions to allow practice on predictable behaviour. User can change variance is ideal.
â€¢	Custom persona creation from uploaded audio/video/transcripts.(Ideal)
3. Feedback Analytics
â€¢	Conversation transcript with timestamps.
â€¢	Performance scoring (confidence, clarity, persuasion).
â€¢	Improvement suggestions with examples.
â€¢	Progress tracking dashboard.
â€¢	Highlight key moments (e.g., objection handling, closing attempts).
4. Training Scenarios
â€¢	Scenario selection (e.g., sales discovery, objection handling, negotiations).
â€¢	Scenario management by administrators or developers too.
5. User Interface
â€¢	Dashboard with scenario and persona selection.
â€¢	Feedback interface.
â€¢	Post-conversation analysis and session reports.
â€¢	Persona management interface.

Non-Functional Requirements
1. Performance
â€¢	Voice response latency < 1.5 seconds.
â€¢	Handle 10-minute conversation sessions.
2. Security
â€¢	Authentication.

Technical Requirements

â€¢	Frontend Layer: React.js web interface, Admin panel.
â€¢	Backend: Python FastAPI.
â€¢	AI/ML: Google Cloud STT (STT), GPT-4/Qwen2.5-0.5B (LLM), Coqui TTS (TTS).
â€¢	Database: PostgreSQL (user data), Redis (session management).
â€¢	Analytics: Custom ML pipeline for feedback.
â€¢	API Layer: FastAPI backend.
â€¢	Core Services: Chat service, configuration, context memory.
â€¢	ML Pipeline: Preprocessing (STT), LLM inference, post-processing, feedback, and any relevant analytics (e.g Usage, System, Progress )
â€¢	TTS Layer: Text-to-speech, emotion-aware TTS.
â€¢	Model Infrastructure including model data: Model cache, tokenizer, persona DB, AV storage.
â€¢	Data Storage: Logs, stats, cache, profile.
â€¢	Utilities: Health monitoring, cleanup cache, download reports/sessions.
â€¢	Output Layer: AI text, AI voice, feedback, session report.




